{"about_the_game":"Meeting Semyon, the game's main character, you would've never paid attention to him. Just an ordinary young man with thousands, even hundreds of thousands of those like him in every ordinary city. But one day something completely unusual happens to him: he falls asleep in a bus in winter and wakes up... in the middle of a hot summer. In front of him is &quot;Sovyonok&quot; - a pioneer camp, behind him is his former life. To understand what happened to him, Semyon will have to get to know the local inhabitants (and maybe even find love), find his way in the complex labyrinth of human relationships and his own problems and solve the camp's mysteries. And answer the main question - how to come back? Should he come back?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Semyon, good end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/b061fe18138d367047280859924a39f0b0cd7a40.jpg"},{"name":"Slavya, good end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/179e98635f852a47d28142dafbae4ecae2788e7c.jpg"},{"name":"Lena, good end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/e5d81227a1082c9c331b0d38839abb8d27df8ef1.jpg"},{"name":"Alisa, good end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/5e797dd8f7f14e5226877409af7eb9107916eef6.jpg"},{"name":"Ulyana, good end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/85c46ab2b2e6b88549bead36b68e50980270325d.jpg"},{"name":"Miku end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/4faff3843c7653b9d1abffcfba0bb953812ebf0f.jpg"},{"name":"??? end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/92c60fcd6e537677572c00f366e628d791340d75.jpg"},{"name":"Harem end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/331470/50ef543cc9137484bd67bf0aa0b3a7d4